name: KillBangMarryGame
skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: kill bang marry
des: There are two parts to this skill. One where you can give Alexa 3 names and she will choose who to kill, bang and marry. Part two is where you can choose from a variety of preset categories and Alexa will give you 3 names to play with.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
